<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-3590] AccessPermission not applied</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3590</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using PdfBox 2.0.3 from maven repository.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I modified a PDF with Adobe Pro to add editable fields that I can edit with PdfBox in JAVA.&lt;br/&gt;
Everything works well but I wanted to set the document as read-only so people downloading the generated pdf could not change values.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So I followed &lt;a href=&quot;https://pdfbox.apache.org/2.0/cookbook/encryption.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://pdfbox.apache.org/2.0/cookbook/encryption.html&lt;/a&gt; but it&apos;s not working.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is my method &lt;a href=&quot;https://gist.github.com/mgohin/b09fed91e7475c09326d1ae25686dcd1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gist.github.com/mgohin/b09fed91e7475c09326d1ae25686dcd1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
